<!-- TIMELINE -->
<section class="timeline">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-img"></div>

      <div class="timeline-content wow fadeInLeft">
        <h2>Ask your question</h2>
        <div class="date">STEP 1</div>
        <p>Add the question describing it as best as possible, add tags to it so that the experts can find it and add a
          reward.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-img"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content wow fadeInRight">
        <h2>See which experts have answered you</h2>
        <div class="date">STEP 2</div>
        <p>Once you have visualized which experts have responded to you, you can pay the reward you promised to be able
          to see their responses.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-img"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content wow fadeInLeft">
        <h2>Choose the best answer</h2>
        <div class="date">STEP 1</div>
        <p>Being able to visualize the answers you are already enabled to choose the best answer and therefore the
          reward will be taken.
          In the event that the time period is met and you have not chosen the best answer, the reward will go to the
          answer with the best rating.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
